<HEADLINE>
<P>
REGISTRATION OF ASSAULT GUNS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The National Rifle Assn. has shown that its understanding of "civil 
disobedience" is about as accurate as its interpretation of the Second 
Amendment. 
</P>
<P>
The basic element, as demonstrated by Thoreau, Gandhi and Dr. Martin Luther 
King Jr., is that you accept the punishment after openly disobeying the "bad" 
law. 
</P>
<P>
Surreptitiously breaking the law, by not registering their assault weapons, has 
another name. It is called "crime," and its practitioners are criminals to the 
same extent as those who they claim to protect us from. 
</P>
