POLLUTION -- ORANGE COUNTY; ORANGE COUNTY -- AGRICULTURE; FERTILIZER; WASTE 
MATERIALS -- DISPOSAL; ALGAE; INVESTIGATIONS; IRVINE CO 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA120790-0081 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 318952 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 7, 1990, Friday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
