-- ARMED FORCES -- KUWAIT; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES -- PERSIAN GULF 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA120790-0125 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 319062 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 7, 1990, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
